### Example 60: Computing Total Volume of Two Boxes (Exact Fractions)

<!-- BUILD: Run this program. Box A has dimensions 3/2 × 2 × 1. Box B has dimensions 5/4 × 3 × 2. Compute the volume of each and the total volume. -->

```scheme
(define vol-a (exact/* (exact/* (exact/rat 3 2) (exact/rat 2 1)) (exact/rat 1 1)))
(define vol-b (exact/* (exact/* (exact/rat 5 4) (exact/rat 3 1)) (exact/rat 2 1)))
(define total-vol (exact/+ vol-a vol-b))

(print \"Box A volume: \" (exact/->string vol-a))
(print \"Box B volume: \" (exact/->string vol-b))
(print \"Total volume: \" (exact/->string total-vol))
```

**Output:**
```
Box A volume: 3/1
Box B volume: 15/2
Total volume: 21/2
```

[VISUAL: Text output showing the three exact volumes (Box A = 3, Box B = 15/2, total = 21/2 = 10.5).]

